{"tid":2218642,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"PCM 話收到風 RTX 3080 同 3090 要回收？？！！","createTime":"2020-09-26T11:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T11:13:40.000Z","uid":270334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b5a1d151d7db44c35cc1da3420ad5fc50c3f2df6","tid":2218642,"uid":270334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azPQwh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FazPQwh3.jpg&h=b9e0710e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb220e39b1d464f59c69cd7a3a6d537bca18b2c6","tid":2218642,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"NEWEGG 撚RAP"},{"pid":"acf93ec062263a8dde05c73769b2abb190a96e20","tid":2218642,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:07:18.000Z","msg":"會係咩問題要回收咁大獲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef82b17151ab79c5689206db65b5846d64508da","tid":2218642,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:08:04.000Z","msg":"關於 RTX 3080 遊戲閃退問題可能與 GPU 背面電容有關<br />\n<br />\nIgor&rsquo;s Lab 針對 RTX 3080 自製卡於遊戲閃退的問題，指出了一個方向：「這可能與 GPU 背面所使用的電容有關。」<br />\n<br />\nIgor 提道這次 NVIDIA 提供給自製卡伙伴的時間較短，僅進行本的通電、電路與功能測試，但實際上機以遊戲進行測試時，部分 OC 版本的自製卡在超過 2GHz 時脈時，則會導致遊戲閃退的狀況發生。<br />\n<br />\n而 NVIDIA 給出的 &ldquo;reference board&rdquo; PG132 參考設計，並於 BOM 表中留著電源穩定、濾波的背面電容選擇性，Base Design 要求 6 組電容處理 NVVDD 與 MSVDD 的濾波、穩壓等設計。<br />\n<br />\nNVIDIA 創始版使用 4 顆 SP-CAPs 與 2 組 MLCC（10 顆）組成，ZOTAC 則選擇 6 顆 POSCAP 設計，至於 ASUS TUF 則全採用 6 組 MLCC 組成。<br />\n<br />\n目前 RTX 3080 的遊戲閃退問題可能根這有關，若玩家有遇到可稍微降低 GPU 時脈約 100 MHz 左右，讓 GPU 自動 Boost 時不會超過 2GHz 的時脈，或者等 NVIDIA、顯卡廠商針對目前狀況來通過韌體、驅動更新解決。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767bb8b00dd069a077e1f353bcee8aeda591657d","tid":2218642,"uid":307673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a28f9f808f24167a3dc1836366f85fe272e044","tid":2218642,"uid":122686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:13:43.000Z","msg":"老黃刀功出事????"},{"pid":"367e04c4827ecece78fb46f8dfd634a2bf81b3f6","tid":2218642,"uid":144323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45a28f9f808f24167a3dc1836366f85fe272e044","tid":2218642,"uid":122686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:13:43.000Z","msg":"老黃刀功出事????"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:15:41.000Z","msg":"好似 FE 無事喎<br />\n<br />\n係其他廠出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c2647cedefce065eb68de30dbcf49f5d3e52bc","tid":2218642,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"姐係d非公oc卡出晒事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a47b5ddcdf7a35289ab254d4e9c5c149feb3a0","tid":2218642,"uid":231743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7c2647cedefce065eb68de30dbcf49f5d3e52bc","tid":2218642,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"姐係d非公oc卡出晒事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:53:03.000Z","msg":"公卡都出事，用左cheap既電容<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c1f4857a5afaada271434c0a744a45055a574b","tid":2218642,"uid":105348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T11:13:40.000Z","msg":"推到pcm 出黎解釋"}]}